title: A picture of me :)
body:
Since you guys always ask to see photos of my beatiful girlfriend and now your asking to see me, I've decided that you guys have deserved the privilage to see my face, so here we are :)

But there is a twist just to spice things up, one of the 4 pictures is me  :)

replies.body: Are we just going to be left guessing, or will you reveal the truth?
If we get it right do we win anything?
You get cuter as the pictures progress, but then I realize it's because of filters/half your face being blocked. However, 4th one you have tats, third one you don't.. is this a timeline or what?
